The paper also uses deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks, which are commonly used in the sub-fields of machine learning and artificial intelligence, hence cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also deals with image processing and analysis, which falls under the sub-field of multimedia, hence cs.MM (Multimedia) is another likely category. Finally, the paper deals with object detection and localization, which is a sub-field of information retrieval, hence cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category.
